#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:3 66c0754094d24ef1877d9f9f0b4de5b5
msgid "Fine-Tuning Walkthrough: VoxCPM 2 on LibriSpeech"
msgstr "微调实战：在 LibriSpeech 上微调 VoxCPM 2"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:5 0e51a445aff04b76be45447956a8c009
msgid ""
"A complete walkthrough: data preparation → training → inference, using the "
"publicly available `LibriSpeech <https://www.openslr.org/12>`_ corpus. The "
"same workflow applies to any comparable speech dataset — just swap the data-"
"preparation step for your own source."
msgstr ""
"完整流程：数据准备 → 微调 → 推理，使用公开的 `LibriSpeech <https://www.openslr.org/12>`_ "
"语料。同类语音数据集均可沿用同一流程 — 只需将数据准备步骤换成你的数据源。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:10 961c051ee0a34359b1cd14b552b52acd
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "准备工作"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:13 4e062de06917469c97199b258c2de92a
msgid "Hardware"
msgstr "硬件要求"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:15 65a54ac2f91b4b79816448f171487401
msgid ""
"Rough estimates with ``batch_size=16`` and ``max_batch_tokens=8192`` on "
"VoxCPM 2. Actual usage depends on audio length and accumulation steps."
msgstr ""
"在 VoxCPM 2 上，``batch_size=16``、``max_batch_tokens=8192`` "
"时的粗略估算；实际占用取决于音频长度与梯度累积步数。"

