msgid "LoRA"
msgstr "LoRA"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:24 b44b223efca84d8b98bdd792dc2048b2
msgid "Single GPU"
msgstr "单卡"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:25 3f758e62a56943a48d5220fcffc9b299
msgid "~40 GB VRAM"
msgstr "约 40 GB 显存"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:26 fe66a94b12714c6a8b0d4a078f9c39a9
msgid "~20 GB VRAM"
msgstr "约 20 GB 显存"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:27 1674e0bda7ea41a58a6fc677e6b70c60
msgid "DDP — additional per-card overhead"
msgstr "DDP — 每卡额外开销"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:28 ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:29
#: a9a907fe152442fa98377366ae4d6548 b8835c8920f947879601a9a851bb8e0f
msgid "+~10 GB"
msgstr "+约 10 GB"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:33 6ea6fbe3b05a410e9c4b395d991b574e
msgid ""
"**DDP extra memory** comes from a per-GPU gradient bucket for ``allreduce`` "
"communication (≈ all trainable params × 4 bytes) plus NCCL buffers. If you "
"hit OOM in DDP, reduce ``batch_size`` or ``max_batch_tokens``."
msgstr ""
"**DDP 额外显存** 来自每张卡用于 ``allreduce`` 的梯度桶（约 可训练参数 × 4 字节）以及 NCCL 缓冲。若 DDP 下 "
"OOM，可降低 ``batch_size`` 或 ``max_batch_tokens``。"

