msgstr "磁盘空间"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:51 902cbb3f79e74f1e8c25e33a697e8289
msgid "~30 GB for ``train-clean-100``; ~5 GB for checkpoints"
msgstr "``train-clean-100`` 约需 30 GB；checkpoint 约 5 GB"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:60 7ce49c3b2d3949aba57b491f76df8843
msgid "Step 1 — Download LibriSpeech"
msgstr "第 1 步：下载 LibriSpeech"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:68 5eff41bc58734d16927bbc3ef69e0018
msgid "The extracted directory layout:"
msgstr "解压后的目录结构："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:82 5f1311e356a94df3b5df617161f6ee08
msgid "Step 2 — Build the JSONL Manifest"
msgstr "第 2 步：生成 JSONL 清单"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:84 32337c0ed65841589de33115d2330bfe
msgid ""
"The training script expects a **JSONL manifest** — one JSON object per line "
"with at minimum an ``audio`` path and a ``text`` transcript."
msgstr "训练脚本需要 **JSONL 清单** — 每行一个 JSON 对象，至少包含 ``audio`` 路径与 ``text`` 转写。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:86 f7139da154fc4be9a0d188b874744838
msgid ""
"Save the script below as ``scripts/prepare_librispeech_manifest.py`` and run"
" it once:"
msgstr "将下方脚本保存为 ``scripts/prepare_librispeech_manifest.py`` 并运行一次："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:125 e3ede2e29f7d4b2fb9614434e685303f
msgid "The resulting manifest looks like:"
msgstr "生成的清单示例如下："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:134 f6621daee19f4d0798a8bbfe8b56806d
msgid ""
"**Why** ``text.capitalize()`` **instead of leaving ALL-CAPS?** VoxCPM's pre-"
"training corpus uses sentence-cased text. Feeding ALL-CAPS transcripts can "
"degrade text adherence at inference time. ``str.capitalize()`` is a simple "
"heuristic; a proper truecasing model gives better results for production "
"use."
msgstr ""
"**为何**用 ``text.capitalize()`` **而不是保留全大写？** VoxCPM "
"预训练语料为句首大写风格。推理时若喂入全大写转写可能损害文本贴合度。``str.capitalize()`` 是简单启发式；生产环境可用专门的 "
"truecasing 模型效果更好。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:139 11340183b895428088c3c66faf8e268f
msgid "Step 3a — Full Fine-Tuning (SFT)"
msgstr "第 3a 步：全量微调（SFT）"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:141 91312f6948e54b0d97f3a8151cbf2e43
msgid ""
"Full fine-tuning updates **all model parameters**. Best for large datasets "
"or significant domain shifts where LoRA capacity is insufficient."
msgstr "全量微调会更新 **全部参数**。适合大数据集或领域偏移明显、LoRA 容量不足的场景。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:144 ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:199
#: 96774bae92f7464cae8b24f2b0b43f3c 9f2f598e0b644b9ea86102b6f171dca4
msgid "Config file"
msgstr "配置文件"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:146 aa58a45f0b7d49f98c5cd109cbbba4f0
msgid "Save as ``conf/librispeech_full.yaml``:"
msgstr "保存为 ``conf/librispeech_full.yaml``："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:178 ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:241
#: 7db31409c7734eabbda0f1fcfc97c5ac a947c0e9124b40ee88568af8c8caa5c2
msgid "Launch"
msgstr "启动命令"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:189 7554aad14b914987baa56c7970d16ee4
msgid ""
"You can also fill in ``CONFIG_PATH``, ``TRAIN_MANIFEST``, and ``BATCH_SIZE``"
" at the top of ``run_train.sh`` and run ``bash run_train.sh``."
msgstr ""
"也可在 ``run_train.sh`` 顶部填写 ``CONFIG_PATH``、``TRAIN_MANIFEST``、``BATCH_SIZE`` "
"后执行 ``bash run_train.sh``。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:194 01315bbfe27c45b68dd9feea6160d9e9
msgid "Step 3b — LoRA Fine-Tuning"
msgstr "第 3b 步：LoRA 微调"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:196 ac9e968231cb4ca8ac0d314df35cee08
msgid ""
"LoRA freezes the base model and trains only a small set of low-rank delta "
"matrices. **Recommended as the default starting point.**"
msgstr "LoRA 冻结基座，仅训练少量低秩增量矩阵。 **建议作为默认起点。**"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:201 1ee74d08ace74cffad90d2fc3818d746
msgid "Save as ``conf/librispeech_lora.yaml``:"
msgstr "保存为 ``conf/librispeech_lora.yaml``："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:250 9b7d000737bb478ba7d1672b082ed6d4
msgid "Step 4 — Monitor Training"
msgstr "第 4 步：观察微调过程"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:259 9ff0d6cbe2c245b2bee6a42d4840a4a5
msgid "Metrics to watch"
msgstr "重点观察哪些指标"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:265 b2c616e175d142e0b68db71965f6a793
msgid "Metric"
msgstr "指标"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:266 6c6bf0a0f6f445a89c0c0f5f0f624230
msgid "Healthy pattern"
msgstr "健康表现"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:267 0508c3c00ef141c2a99aa9f9c985dd8b
msgid "``loss/diff``"
msgstr "``loss/diff``"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:268 6baa8a9844a149db80a7b8bc5cebfc88
msgid "Decreases steadily; flattens as convergence approaches"
msgstr "平稳下降；接近收敛时趋于平缓"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:269 d36f3132bf4646ab912feb4735f476c2
msgid "``loss/stop``"
msgstr "``loss/stop``"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:270 fb7e673250b7441db0aa1a4d79dc79b3
msgid "Drops quickly in the first 100–200 steps, then stays low"
msgstr "前 100–200 步快速下降，之后保持较低"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:271 0f1cb4a7ee084730b8d08413594eb0c7
msgid "``grad_norm``"
msgstr "``grad_norm``"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:272 46a3107bff1f43b08f9213ccd0746ad9
msgid "Stays roughly in the 0.3–2.0 range; occasional spikes are fine"
msgstr "大致落在 0.3–2.0；偶发尖峰可接受"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:273 ef0447362901493bb49d38ed46223617
msgid "``lr``"
msgstr "``lr``"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:274 ae1109c096694509aea48423052177ea
msgid "Cosine warm-up then decay"
msgstr "余弦 warm-up 后衰减"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:275 4929d03d6de8415f8a986a4e940dac33
msgid "``val/loss``"
msgstr "``val/loss``"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:276 7ba4fa56f04c42da857277ead5117233
msgid "Tracks training loss; **stop if it rises while train loss keeps falling**"
msgstr "随训练损失变化； **若训练损失仍降而验证损失上升，应停止**"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:279 3ca22b704e5b45ccb04f60a88b462471
msgid "When to stop"
msgstr "什么时候可以停止训练"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:281 eee67d82f69e46b98e429be5032c756b
msgid ""
"**1–2 epochs is almost always enough** for TTS fine-tuning. The best "
"checkpoint is often not the final one."
msgstr "TTS 微调 **通常 1–2 个 epoch 足够**。最佳 checkpoint 往往不在最后。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:283 ec17f9b4963141a696e6cb4ca44fd3ea
msgid "Use ``valid_interval: 50`` and ``save_interval: 50`` for rollback options."
msgstr "使用 ``valid_interval: 50`` 与 ``save_interval: 50`` 便于回滚。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:284 005641ab2ef2495cbc07a594fa9c2a93
msgid "Pick the checkpoint where ``val/loss`` was lowest."
msgstr "选取 ``val/loss`` 最低时对应的 checkpoint。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:285 38c660939cb54b6d9d681df633cea332
msgid ""
"If you do not have a val manifest, evaluate a handful of checkpoints in the "
"convergence zone with the inference script and pick the best-sounding one."
msgstr "若无验证清单，可在收敛区间取若干 checkpoint 用推理脚本试听，选听感最佳者。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:289 896a8008555d43838cc684744dae4fd0
msgid ""
"If ``val/loss`` starts rising while ``train/loss`` keeps falling, **stop "
"immediately** and roll back. This is the classic overfitting signature for "
"TTS models: the model will start ignoring input text and generate the same "
"voice pattern regardless of what you type."
msgstr ""
"若 ``val/loss`` 开始上升而 ``train/loss`` 仍在下降，请**立即停止**并回退。这是 TTS "
"模型典型的过拟合信号：模型会忽略输入文本，无论输入什么都生成相似的音色模式。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:294 db34867920fa4076b0dc965e86a55c54
msgid "Step 5 — Inference"
msgstr "第 5 步：推理验证"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:297 d1cdc89667034aae8ca5e41912229adc
msgid "SFT checkpoint"
msgstr "SFT checkpoint 推理"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:316 c21b5e08c42a47258e74ba606798398c
msgid "LoRA checkpoint"
msgstr "LoRA checkpoint 推理"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:325 4eae49b783424ebc891c96321625c4b8
msgid "To batch-evaluate and compare multiple checkpoints:"
msgstr "批量评估并对比多个 checkpoint："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:339 c4de92e0331a43f7bc534f6effc97f45
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "常见问题排查"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:342 10df4b74f4a142e49b336d20a3cdb7f5
msgid "Out-of-memory (OOM)"
msgstr "显存不足（OOM）"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:344 4f9ff0c98c3545b99773d263a76eefe1
msgid ""
"LibriSpeech clips vary in duration (2 s – 35 s). ``max_batch_tokens`` "
"already filters the longest ones. If OOM persists, try:"
msgstr "LibriSpeech 片段时长不一（2–35 s）。``max_batch_tokens`` 会过滤最长部分。若仍 OOM，可尝试："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:356 a1bc66cf9f0544a684cd0b8cbb486892
msgid "Loss does not decrease"
msgstr "损失不下降"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:358 7c35a27bf11b4478b483e84e94b06001
msgid ""
"Verify that audio paths in the manifest are correct and all files are "
"readable."
msgstr "确认清单中的音频路径正确且文件可读。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:359 75abcb1b25334a6983a374a65df42953
msgid ""
"LibriSpeech FLAC files are 16 kHz; keep ``sample_rate: 48000`` — the "
"dataloader resamples automatically for VoxCPM 2."
msgstr ""
"LibriSpeech FLAC 为 16 kHz；保持 ``sample_rate: 48000`` 即可 — 数据加载器会为 VoxCPM 2 "
"自动重采样。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:360 b767082e56474580b74c238374bd1ad0
msgid "Check that transcripts are sentence-cased, not ALL-CAPS."
msgstr "确认转写为句首大写，而非全大写。"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:363 6278c384cc574463938f0709a87b341a
msgid "Generated audio ignores input text"
msgstr "生成音频忽略输入文本"

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:365 24684926f16641b39bfedab5c1f2440b
msgid "Classic overfitting symptom. Roll back to an earlier checkpoint:"
msgstr "典型过拟合表现。请回退到较早的 checkpoint："

#: ../../finetuning/walkthrough.rst:376 52aa4738a2e248c9baf8e5bd931e2165
msgid ""
"For future runs: always provide a ``val_manifest``, use ``valid_interval: "
"50``, and stop when ``val/loss`` turns upward. Keeping training within 1–3 "
"epochs generally avoids this problem entirely."
msgstr ""
"后续训练：始终提供 ``val_manifest``，使用 ``valid_interval: 50``，并在 ``val/loss`` "
"拐头向上时停止。将训练控制在 1–3 个 epoch 内通常可避免此问题。"

